            <p class="page-subtitle" data-i18n="careers.subtitle"></p>

            <div class="careers-content">
                <div class="why-us-section">
                    <h2>Why Legacy Concierge?</h2>
                    <p>Legacy Concierge delivers unmatched care for elite clients. We hire top nurses and caregivers to drive excellence. Our 97% retention rate reflects a supportive culture and a dedicated team, ensuring nurses and caregivers thrive.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>EXCEPTIONAL RETENTION:</strong> Our 97% retention rate reflects a supportive culture where caregivers thrive.</li>
                        <li><strong>SELECTIVE HIRING:</strong> We recruit only the best, connecting elite nurses with premier opportunities.</li>
                        <li><strong>EXPERIENCED PROFESSIONALS:</strong> Join our seasoned team to deliver unparalleled care.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="benefits-section">
                    <h2>Benefits</h2>
                    <p>Legacy Concierge fuels your success with top rewards and support.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>HIGH PAY:</strong> Earn what your skills deserve.</li>
                        <li><strong>FLEXIBLE SHIFTS:</strong> Pick schedules that work for you.</li>
                        <li><strong>CAREER SUPPORT:</strong> Gain training, mentorship, and benefits to excel.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="apply" class="contact-form careers-apply">
                <h3>Ready to Join?</h3>
                <p>Apply now—be part of Legacy Concierge's elite nursing and prestige care team.</p>
                <form>
                    <input type="text" name="first-name" placeholder="First Name" required>
                    <input type="text" name="last-name" placeholder="Last Name" required>
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
                    <input type="text" name="phone" placeholder="Your Phone">
                    <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your Message" rows="6" required></textarea>
                    <label for="resume">Attach Resume</label>
                    <input type="file" id="resume" name="resume">
                    <button type="submit" class="cta-button">Submit Application</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>
